Title: Fixed slow GUI when using custom host attributes from versions <= 1.5
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1594641423
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.0.0i1

Every GUI page loaded more slowly if you had configured custom host attributes in versions <=1.5.
The slowdown effect scaled with the number of host tag groups, especially when the number of groups exceeded 100.
